When Jesus said in the Sermon on the Mount, “Blessed are the meek, for they shall inherit the earth,” He wasn’t talking of this broken planet but the promised New Earth. #Shorts​​​​​​​​​​​​​​ #YouTubeShorts​​​​​​​​​​​​​​ 

Listen as Pastor Ted Wilson shares insights about the third blessing from Thoughts from the Mount of Blessing by Adventist pioneer Ellen White: https://youtu.be/4PQSSCKPpXE
